Preconditions:
- The input array `arr` is not null.
- The length of the input array `arr` is greater than or equal to 1.
- All elements in the input array `arr` are positive integers.

Postconditions:
- The value of the first element in the modified array `arr` is 1.
- The absolute difference between any two adjacent elements in the modified array `arr` is less than or equal to 1.
- The maximum possible value of an element in the modified array `arr` is returned as an integer.